node.text:
Diving headfirst into the weekend like… ☁️Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @globefever 

Wingsuit flying (or wingsuiting) is the sport of flying through the air using a wingsuit which adds surface area to the human body to enable a significant increase in lift. 

This wingsuit flight was shoot in Montserrat Natural Park, a multi-peaked mountain range near Barcelona, in Catalonia, Spain.

"Montserrat" literally means "serrated (like the common handsaw) mountain" in Catalan. It describes its peculiar aspect with a multitude of rock formations that are visible from a great distance. The mountain is composed of strikingly pink conglomerate, a form of sedimentary rock.

📽 @daniroman_ @fredfugen @vincent.cotte @bras.noir
📍Montserrant, Spain

Autumn walks in Finland 🍁✨ Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @globefever 

Have you seen visit this country in the fall season before?

Fall leaf colours, also known as "Ruska" to locals, characterises this season months in Finland. Landscapes are painted in vivid yellows, reds and browns, making every walk and hike even more magical.

Which picture is your favorite? Tag someone who loves @nature!

📷 @jukkarisikko
